data.description: Welcome to Unit #120 at Edina Brookside! Step inside to discover the carefree lifestyle offered by this exceptional home, enhanced with freshly painted interior and new flooring. The spacious living room offers new neutral carpet, and is open to the dining room. Sliders lead to the inviting three-season porch, where you can enjoy sipping your morning coffee or dining al fresco on breezy summer evenings. The functional kitchen is complete with sleek white cabinetry, new flooring and great workspace. The dining room is adjacent for your serving ease! The owner's bedroom is spacious and bright, with a wall of windows, new soft-on-your-feet carpet, and a large walk-in closet. The owner's bath has a large step-in shower, a vanity, and ceramic tile accents. A second bedroom has sunny windows, a double closet, and a ceramic tiled full bath nearby. One heated garage stall + storage unit! Amenities include an indoor heated pool, party/amusement room. Great location, an easy commute to downtown!
